27,53,878],"popularity":16.2528,"vote_count":8234,"poster_path":"/sQckQRt17VaWbo39GIu0TMOiszq.jpg","release_date":"2002-10-31","vote_average":7.237,"backdrop_path":"/aJFwk1clMal1prxAvKAgHxKPAf.jpg","original_title":"28 Days Later","original_language":"en"},{"id":176,"adult":false,"title":"Saw","video":false,"overview":"Two men wake up to find themselves shackled in a grimy, abandoned bathroom. As they struggle to comprehend their predicament, they discover a disturbing tape left behind by the sadistic mastermind known as Jigsaw. With a chilling voice and cryptic instructions, Jigsaw informs them that they must partake in a gruesome game in order to secure their freedom.","genre_ids":[27,9648,80],"popularity":7.5359,"vote_count":9876,"poster_path":"/rLNSOudrayDBo1uqXjrhxcjODIC.jpg","release_date":"2004-10-01","vote_average":7.419,"backdrop_path":"/ok4ot3YbfDYZcINXf91JUfq3maB.jpg","original_title":"Saw","original_language":"en"},{"id":196,"adult":false,"title":"Back to the Future Part III","video":false,"overview":"The final installment finds Marty digging the trusty DeLorean out of a mineshaft and looking for Doc in the Wild West of 1885. But when their time machine breaks down, the travelers are stranded in a land of spurs. More problems arise when Doc falls for pretty schoolteacher Clara Clayton, and Marty tangles with Buford Tannen.","genre_ids":[12,35,878],"popularity":6.747,"vote_count":11311,"poster_path":"/crzoVQnMzIrRfHtQw0tLBirNfVg.jpg","release_date":"1990-05-25","vote_average":7.489,"backdrop_path":"/AtF7TESJEMmImBRUj9Z7HmW2ZH0.jpg","original_title":"Back to the Future Part III","original_language":"en"},{"id":214,"adult":false,"title":"Saw III","video":false,"overview":"Jigsaw has disappeared. Along with his new apprentice Amanda, the puppet-master behind the cruel, intricate games that have terrified a community and baffled police has once again eluded capture and vanished. While city detectives scrambles to locate him, Doctor Lynn Denlon and Jeff Reinhart are unaware that they are about to become the latest pawns on his vicious chessboard.","genre_ids":[27,53,80],"popularity":4.2635,"vote_count":4850,"poster_path":"/4iO9n24Rb10peXV0JH2EldIOrAp.jpg","release_date":"2006-10-26","vote_average":6.419,"backdrop_path":"/qx8Pb3nVnHLBizI9792pbRN5nnm.jpg","original_title":"Saw III","original_language":"en"},{"id":590003,"adult":false,"title":"A Living Dog","video":false,"overview":"The war between mankind and intelligent machines has begun - and the machines are winning. Tomasz is a deserter who tries to hide as far away from the battle as possible.  In the vast emptiness of northern Scandinavia he meets Lilja, the last survivor of a resistance group, who is determined to fight the superior machines. With every minute that passes the machines get closer, searching for the last remains of the human race. And the enemy doesn't just shoot on sight - their perfect sensors are programmed to recognize human voice patterns.  So if you speak or even whisper - you die.","genre_ids":[878,28,53],"popularity":0.1779,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/kkpeYDMS0LPLPtQveJGvkLMk4V8.jpg","release_date":"2019-09-07","vote_average":5.3,"backdrop_path":"/eECrrbuwrf4Xjc6i5rLv3yijMjV.jpg","original_title":"A Living Dog","original_language":"en"},{"id":590223,"adult":false,"title":"Love and Monsters","video":false,"overview":"Seven years since the Monsterpocalypse began, Joel Dawson has been living underground in order to survive. But after reconnecting over radio with his high school girlfriend Aimee, Joel decides to venture out to reunite with her, despite all the dangerous monsters that stand in his way.","genre_ids":[35,12,878],"popularity":4.0296,"vote_count":4346,"poster_path":"/718NnyxyQuBQcGWt9sdelA1Zc3h.jpg","release_date":"2020-10-16","vote_average":7.275,"backdrop_path":"/lA5fOBqTOQBQ1s9lEYYPmNXoYLi.jpg","original_title":"Love and Monsters","original_language":"en"},{"id":419261,"adult":false,"title":"Earthtastrophe","video":false,"overview":"In a white hot flash of light, and with no warning, one minute our moon is there, the next it's gone. Then, a second flash. And that's the last thing anyone on Earth can remember. 11 months later, it's not post- apocalyptic; it's apocalyptic as Earth has been sucked through a wormhole, literally ripping our planet from the inside out. With bizarre disasters and civilization collapsing, our heroes must find a way to survive and get to \"safe ground\" before it's too late.","genre_ids":[878,10770],"popularity":2.667,"vote_count":44,"poster_path":"/PdO6DOQktCGtPeZRrtOZhtvjWf.jpg","release_date":"2016-03-05","vote_average":4.6,"backdrop_path":"/q9VrDrEO55HppFzEchAmHfGH1Qw.jpg","original_title":"Earthtastrophe","original_language":"en"},{"id":947924,"adult":false,"title":"Běžci","video":false,"overview":"After the global collapse of civilization, part of Europe remains uninhabitable. People form small groups, surviving in safe zones separated from each other by strips of land where uncontrolled military technology creates deadly \"traps.\" The only ones who can cross the dangerous territories are the \"runners.\" The fate of several people who have decided to find a safe place for a new life depends on one of them.","genre_ids":[878,18],"popularity":0.171,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"2014-04-23","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Běžci","original_language":"cs"},{"id":1291785,"adult":false,"title":"Twilight of the Warriors: Dragon Throne","video":false,"overview":"The second installment of the Twilight of the Warriors trilogy.\r In 1950s Hong Kong, brothers Lui Cheng-tung and Chen Jim fled to the lawless Kowloon Walled City at the peak of their careers. They endured hardships, waiting for a chance to reclaim their losses. During this time, they encountered a man who significantly influenced their struggle to regain what they had lost.","genre_ids":[28,53,80,12],"popularity":0.7488,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/5D4Ss05hIbV7E8fjO4ZThLbGa6J.jpg","release_date":"","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"九龍城寨之龍頭","original_language":"cn"},{"id":1291787,"adult":false,"title":"Twilight of the Warriors: The Final Chapter","video":false,"overview":"The final installment of the Twilight of the Warriors trilogy.","genre_ids":[28,53,80],"popularity":0.2766,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/5D4Ss05hIbV7E8fjO4ZThLbGa6J.jpg","release_date":"","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"九龍城寨之終章","original_language":"cn"},{"id":646,"adult":false,"title":"Dr. No","video":false,"overview":"Agent 007 battles mysterious Dr. No, a scientific genius bent on destroying the U.S. space program. As the countdown to disaster begins, Bond must go to Jamaica, where he encounters beautiful Honey Ryder, to confront a megalomaniacal villain in his massive island headquarters.","genre_ids":[12,28,53],"popularity":7.2117,"vote_count":3954,"poster_path":"/f9HsemSsBEHN5eoMble1bj6fDxs.jpg","release_date":"1962-10-07","vote_average":6.99,"backdrop_path":"/ptcXbbxTyjHfEE4d4QocNP0YQct.jpg","original_title":"Dr. No","original_language":"en"},{"id":657,"adult":false,"title":"From Russia with Love","video":false,"overview":"Agent 007 is back in the second installment of the James Bond series, this time battling a secret crime organization known as SPECTRE. Russians Rosa Klebb and Kronsteen are out to snatch a decoding device known as the Lektor, using the ravishing Tatiana to lure Bond into helping them. Bond willingly travels to meet Tatiana in Istanbul, where he must rely on his wits to escape with his life in a series of deadly encounters with the enemy.","genre_ids":[28,53,12],"popularity":6.5294,"vote_count":3278,"poster_path":"/zx4V17FP8oclNvOpTgs2iCCtiYk.jpg","release_date":"1963-10-10","vote_average":7.065,"backdrop_path":"/8JMiQa0OqsCYvbNUrQIrMzwV7g2.jpg","original_title":"From Russia with Love","original_language":"en"},{"id":658,"adult":false,"title":"Goldfinger","video":false,"overview":"Special agent 007 comes face to face with one of the most notorious villains of all time, and now he must outwit and outgun the powerful tycoon to prevent him from cashing in on a devious scheme to raid Fort Knox -- and obliterate the world's economy.","genre_ids":[12,28,53],"popularity":6.2145,"vote_count":3869,"poster_path":"/aKNFzaqQgPzsGXnsMc4kJH5hFIV.jpg","release_date":"1964-09-20","vote_average":7.355,"backdrop_path":"/f1Is9VLQZSRpeLMU7mIcj5aXclt.jpg","original_title":"Goldfinger","original_language":"en"},{"id":662,"adult":false,"title":"La Jetée","video":false,"overview":"A man confronts his past during an experiment that attempts to find a solution to the problems of a post-apocalyptic world caused by a world war.","genre_ids":[18,10749,878],"popularity":3.3202,"vote_count":970,"poster_path":"/elGidsRHXkk8UyrtLbcMhaptDyp.jpg","release_date":"1962-02-16","vote_average":7.883,"backdrop_path":"/3Z2OhNVU0FhxGZJIq6Gn32UNoKu.jpg","original_title":"La Jetée","original_language":"fr"},{"id":663,"adult":false,"title":"Saw IV","video":false,"overview":"Despite Jigsaw's death, and in order to save the lives of two of his colleagues, Lieutenant Rigg is forced to take part in a new game, which promises to test him to the limit.","genre_ids":[27,53,80],"popularity":5.0904,"vote_count":4029,"poster_path":"/ku1QdCXOU4ckz3zxLLlis8MIJVm.jpg","release_date":"2007-10-25","vote_average":6.167,"backdrop_path":"/3lrNJ5jNqKq9UpQrXo8FNFzyoE4.jpg","original_title":"Saw IV","original_language":"en"},{"id":667,"adult":false,"title":"You Only Live Twice","video":false,"overview":"A mysterious spacecraft captures Russian and American space capsules and brings the two superpowers to the brink of war. James Bond investigates the case in Japan and comes face to face with his archenemy Blofeld.","genre_ids":[28,53,12],"popularity":7.1355,"vote_count":2402,"poster_path":"/fdRbvRcEXcf2rC4ghLFZzCWPSmB.jpg","release_date":"1967-06-13","vote_average":6.593,"backdrop_path":"/cpZAXIYA0lkZMpAt7d1MmH8ojNV.jpg","original_title":"You Only Live Twice","original_language":"en"},{"id":668,"adult":false,"title":"On Her Majesty's Secret Service","video":false,"overview":"With the help of Marc-Ange Draco, head of the Unione Corse crime syndicate, and Draco's troubled daughter Tracy, James Bond tracks his archnemesis, Ernst Stravro Blofeld, to a mountaintop retreat in the Swiss Alps, where he is training an army of beautiful, lethal women.","genre_ids":[12,28,53],"popularity":5.3271,"vote_count":2077,"poster_path":"/m3KfbxvqaiAvRJ6MpguA3GuLdDQ.jpg","release_date":"1969-12-18","vote_average":6.562,"backdrop_path":"/58pMrmwwcKamJIdjUlinE6QX1Fs.jpg","original_title":"On Her Majesty's Secret Service","original_language":"en"},{"id":682,"adult":false,"title":"The Man with the Golden Gun","video":false,"overview":"Cool government operative James Bond searches for a stolen invention that can turn the sun's heat into a destructive weapon. He soon crosses paths with the menacing Francisco Scaramanga, a hitman so skilled he has a seven-figure working fee. Bond then joins forces with the swimsuit-clad Mary Goodnight, and together they track Scaramanga to a Thai tropical isle hideout where the killer-for-hire lures the slick spy into a deadly maze for a final duel.","genre_ids":[12,28,53],"popularity":4.9709,"vote_count":2220,"poster_path":"/xVkbKwGnBVNQ122GN5bCTMyPbWz.jpg","release_date":"1974-12-04","vote_average":6.456,"backdrop_path":"/3tpNEbRahT8smy7RraaWa0xg9Gv.jpg","original_title":"The Man with the Golden Gun","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt10548174","twitter_id":"28YearsLaterMov","facebook_id":"28yearslaterofficial","wikidata_id":"Q125392328","instagram_id":"28yearslatermovie","metacritic_id":"movie/28-years-later","mydramalist_id":"390786","rotten_tomatoes_id":"m/28_years_later"},"social_ids":{"twitter":"28YearsLaterMov","facebook":"28yearslaterofficial","instagram":"28yearslatermovie"},"gdvg_id":102175,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_e